Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.44,0:02:26.65,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,あのあのどんな色が　今ですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.79,0:02:29.19,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,笑顔のホワイト　涙のブルー
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.46,0:02:31.96,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,重ねてみたとき
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.12,0:02:37.45,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,本日晴天なりっ　キャンパスに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.56,0:02:39.92,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,ミルクのアイス　ラムネごくん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.17,0:02:42.73,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,元気にカラートッピング
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.85,0:02:46.56,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,おーい！　ラブ描き·ぷりーす
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.80,0:02:52.71,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,みんなの似顔絵コンテスト
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.60,0:02:59.92,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,よーし！　後で「ぷんっ」怒らないでね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.19,0:03:05.05,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,スイッチ押されたら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.24,0:03:07.17,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,わっはっは～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.32,0:03:13.49,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,なんかいいキモチ　なればいいカンジ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.73,0:03:17.93,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,競争だ！　いち早くリンゴ食べよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.06,0:03:24.21,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,そうじゃないんだよ　躁でいいんだよ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:28.88,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,果物はモデルさん
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.11,0:03:36.94,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,さあデッサンしましょうか　宿題だよん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.44,0:02:26.65,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,請問請問　現在是什麼顏色呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.79,0:02:29.19,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,笑容的白色　淚水的藍色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.46,0:02:31.96,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,將它們重疊在一起看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.12,0:02:37.45,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,今天天氣晴朗　外出郊遊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.56,0:02:39.92,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,進行冰牛奶彈珠汽水特訓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.17,0:02:42.73,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,代表精神的顏色正充沛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.85,0:02:46.56,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,喂－！　喜歡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.80,0:02:52.71,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,請來進行大家的肖像畫素描比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.60,0:02:59.92,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,好－吧！　之後可別「砰」的一下就生氣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.19,0:03:05.05,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,被人按下按鈕時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.24,0:03:07.17,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,哇哈哈～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.32,0:03:13.49,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得只要開心就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.73,0:03:17.93,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,比賽吧　看誰蘋果吃得快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.06,0:03:24.21,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那樣　急躁起來好嗎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:28.88,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,水果便是模特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.11,0:03:36.94,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,來　開始素描吧　這是作業哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,GO
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,四
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.00,0:00:03.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:04.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:05.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.82,0:00:33.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.71,0:00:46.93,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,今天運勢最佳的是水瓶座
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.14,0:00:48.65,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,日間的努力被認可
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.79,0:00:50.07,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎能更進一步
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.41,0:00:53.36,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,雙魚座的環境有改善的徵兆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.70,0:00:55.06,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,向父母求助的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.30,0:00:57.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個節目好久沒有看了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.16,0:01:01.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,待在家裡的時候不會起這麼早的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.33,0:00:59.49,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,白羊座  今天夢想似乎和你若即若離
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.69,0:01:01.48,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,還是不要太過勉強為好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.46,0:01:04.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  作上學準備的時候總是錯過
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.31,0:01:06.49,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,金牛座  注意不要亂花錢…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.19,0:01:06.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的運勢…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.12,0:01:10.25,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,巨蟹座似乎需要小心注意…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.59,0:01:22.59,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an6}今天的運勢\N射手座\N很不好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.87,0:01:21.18,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,…反而接二連三地有事件
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.49,0:01:23.94,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,靜下心來深呼吸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.00,0:01:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.66,0:01:26.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又錯過了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.48,0:01:26.72,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼大家  今天也請多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.51,0:01:34.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.00,0:01:37.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮  早安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.60,0:01:38.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很冷吧  快進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.12,0:01:40.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.55,0:01:43.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  天氣預報說會下雪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.85,0:01:46.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,或許會下雪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.93,0:01:47.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.05,0:01:53.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  新式的手機看著真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.69,0:01:55.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮  你要買手機嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.80,0:01:56.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.84,0:01:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果誰買了送給我 我就要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.11,0:02:01.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這廣闊的世界中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.31,0:02:04.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定有人願意買任何東西給我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.53,0:02:07.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮  要走了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.02,0:02:09.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  由乃  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.84,0:03:45.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「1月11日  冬日的剪貼畫」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.86,0:03:47.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.91,0:03:52.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,畫這些東西的時候知了還在大合唱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.89,0:03:55.38,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（暖陽莊）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.55,0:03:58.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,記得麼  就是在小宮的房間裡大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:04:00.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿嘿  記得記得
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.45,0:04:02.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那真有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.70,0:04:04.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.60,0:04:05.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:07.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尋學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.31,0:04:08.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:11.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.18,0:04:14.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英學姐  早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.28,0:04:14.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再一次地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.24,0:04:18.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家新年好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.59,0:04:21.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮  你這話我差不多聽了十回了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.90,0:04:24.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天初詣的時候你就說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.90,0:04:24.03,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（初詣：新年第一次參拜神社）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:25.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧神社不是那麼擁擠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.80,0:04:27.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才不用急急忙忙地參拜了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:29.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都是便裝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.89,0:04:32.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吉野老師倒是穿著和服來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.01,0:04:34.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是cosplay女王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.11,0:04:37.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過老師求到的籤可是「凶」喲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.90,0:04:40.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還打算將它放在嘴裡用舌頭打結
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.08,0:04:43.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃你的籤是大吉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.19,0:04:46.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也不能因為這個而大意喲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.01,0:04:48.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「好事多磨」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.71,0:04:49.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.97,0:04:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.53,0:04:54.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.95,0:04:55.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快點快點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.22,0:04:59.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那中午見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.66,0:05:00.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.18,0:05:01.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.87,0:05:02.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來的那堂課
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.58,0:05:03.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說要換教室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.87,0:05:04.60,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.91,0:05:05.65,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,沒聽說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.48,0:05:06.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼說來 由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.87,0:05:07.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作業怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.02,0:05:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作業？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.72,0:05:10.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.17,0:05:13.17,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（美術科  1-A）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.59,0:05:17.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家早安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:19.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,寒假過得開心嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.51,0:05:23.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老師的寒假過得非常的充實
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.68,0:05:26.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和朋友講電話啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.77,0:05:28.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去唱卡拉OK啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.10,0:05:32.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,新年穿著漂亮的和服去參加初詣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.25,0:05:37.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到處躲著為了壓歲錢來死纏爛打的侄兒侄女
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.87,0:05:41.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為 即使我向別人討壓歲錢也絲毫不為過的說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.88,0:05:43.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他們這樣做真的很失禮是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.55,0:05:44.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧  大家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.35,0:05:47.66,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,今天開始又會是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.06,0:05:50.12,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.79,0:05:49.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作業怎麼辦呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.55,0:05:50.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.48,0:05:55.30,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,帶了作業來的同學  請在下午的班會課之前交上來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.54,0:05:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很難得一副心不在焉的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.15,0:05:52.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.13,0:05:54.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼忘記了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:05:58.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在再怎麼拼命也沒用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.30,0:06:00.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,過會兒交不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.75,0:06:03.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候你的籤不是大吉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.77,0:06:04.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.64,0:06:09.59,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,等候的人會到來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.98,0:06:10.90,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,做生意  可盈利\N宜經商
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.18,0:06:12.36,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,打官司  勝訴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.92,0:06:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.65,0:06:16.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.43,0:06:17.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,開始上課了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.30,0:06:22.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:24.40,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}縱橫透視畫法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:30.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.15,0:06:32.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的課就到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:41.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.28,0:06:42.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吉野屋老師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:43.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.68,0:06:44.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  由乃同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.19,0:06:46.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.66,0:06:47.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:48.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.71,0:06:50.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作業沒有及時交…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.85,0:06:53.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想第一節實習課的時候能趕上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.86,0:06:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能讓我那時候交麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.84,0:06:57.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.67,0:06:59.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.02,0:07:01.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.49,0:07:03.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.89,0:07:05.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.05,0:07:12.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來「好事多磨」說的就是這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.05,0:07:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,終於到午休時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃  去吃午飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.89,0:07:22.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.12,0:07:24.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…去拿一下留在家裡的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.29,0:07:26.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮你先去食堂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:29.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.43,0:07:31.46,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（暖陽莊）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.10,0:07:51.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  已經沒有時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.58,0:07:57.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有這些的話看著可能稍顯單薄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.70,0:08:03.22,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（新年好  今年還請多多關照）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.70,0:08:03.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老師什麼時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.98,0:08:05.05,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（我要加油！！）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.31,0:08:07.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,新年好  今年還請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.26,0:08:08.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.23,0:08:10.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:13.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  這個或許用得上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:15.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.34,0:08:17.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,copy來得及嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.57,0:08:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～  只有兩分鐘了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.91,0:08:28.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.94,0:08:29.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:31.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,加油  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.45,0:08:32.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.81,0:08:34.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.59,0:08:36.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,終點就在眼前了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.58,0:08:38.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好難為情的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.99,0:08:43.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.41,0:08:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.91,0:08:57.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼班會課就到這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.46,0:08:59.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪也積了不少了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:02.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家回家的時候要當心腳下喲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:02.82,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（班會主題  聯絡事項  當心感冒）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.13,0:09:06.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:07.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.20,0:09:09.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作業交晚了對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.31,0:09:11.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…是我的作業
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.15,0:09:15.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.98,0:09:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,確實收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.59,0:09:23.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.35,0:09:24.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.30,0:09:26.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那是作業？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:28.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還真趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.76,0:09:29.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.55,0:09:31.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回家後火速趕出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.12,0:09:33.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,午休的時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.29,0:09:33.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.29,0:09:35.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.58,0:09:37.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子好餓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.67,0:09:38.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拿著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.19,0:09:38.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給你的獎賞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.08,0:09:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.79,0:09:43.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.29,0:09:44.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:47.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尋學姐要減肥所以分給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.82,0:09:48.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.71,0:09:51.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,實際上是擔心由乃趕不回來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.91,0:09:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從自己的飯團裡給你留了一個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.65,0:09:55.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.63,0:09:58.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天輪到我們打掃衛生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.48,0:09:59.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快點吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.81,0:10:00.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.62,0:10:09.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快點弄完了  去打雪仗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.81,0:10:10.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.63,0:10:14.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.05,0:10:16.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都已經積了這麼厚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:18.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還誰的腳印都沒有留下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.65,0:10:20.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這一大片的雪都可以一個人獨享了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:21.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.31,0:10:22.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.96,0:10:23.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尋學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.81,0:10:24.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.74,0:10:25.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.69,0:10:27.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說今天輪到你們打掃衛生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.59,0:10:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得應該會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.20,0:10:30.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要我們幫忙嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.51,0:10:31.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  謝謝好意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.77,0:10:34.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思這裡就交給在下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:40.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.74,0:10:42.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:44.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,藝術創作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.35,0:10:46.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  感覺不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.56,0:10:48.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.00,0:10:49.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.89,0:10:51.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼過會兒見了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.43,0:10:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:54.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.23,0:10:57.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我錯過道謝的機會了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.46,0:10:58.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.44,0:11:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還不能過來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.21,0:11:01.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.34,0:11:05.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今年的首次創作活動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.33,0:11:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.91,0:11:11.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Love & Peace嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.12,0:11:13.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是宮子的作風呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.67,0:11:15.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.58,0:11:17.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,P-I-E-C-E
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.89,0:11:19.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,碎片？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.35,0:11:29.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那些孩子還沒有回來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正盡情地玩雪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.99,0:11:34.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,年輕還真是好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.10,0:11:38.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小時侯下雪了真是很開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.60,0:11:39.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,無條件的開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.06,0:11:41.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也根本沒有心思去學習什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.23,0:11:43.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玩些什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.72,0:11:44.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和由乃她們一樣喲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.16,0:11:46.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,堆雪人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.67,0:11:47.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打雪仗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.16,0:11:49.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  也玩過雪橇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.95,0:11:50.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.17,0:11:53.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英那時很意外地是個普通人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.02,0:11:56.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你這麼說好像我現在是個怪人一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.79,0:11:57.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.71,0:12:01.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為你小時侯也和現在一樣cool呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.18,0:12:03.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.68,0:12:05.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我很cool嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.92,0:12:07.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…尋你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.67,0:12:09.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我很喜歡雪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.36,0:12:11.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但不喜歡把自己弄得濕漉漉的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.02,0:12:14.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你想  頭髮受潮後就像快要炸開來了似的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.17,0:12:17.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  實際上是想玩雪的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.41,0:12:19.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,冬天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.61,0:12:21.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是喜歡在暖爐邊上暖洋洋地待著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.14,0:12:24.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英你現在也是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.21,0:12:25.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.52,0:12:26.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是上了年紀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.25,0:12:28.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.31,0:12:30.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,熱茶真好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.57,0:12:31.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.74,0:12:33.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.13,0:12:46.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,飯團的事我得去尋學姐那裡道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.38,0:12:48.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.02,0:12:51.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮你是在期待什麼東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.52,0:12:52.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.49,0:12:53.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,若是能有一杯熱茶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:54.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,暖烘烘的炕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.82,0:12:57.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有點心和蜜橘我就很開心了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.48,0:13:06.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.39,0:13:08.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再一次新年的祝福問候…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.99,0:13:10.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮  那就是第十一回了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.37,0:13:11.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.95,0:13:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.33,0:13:15.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我還沒有道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.24,0:13:16.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才回來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:17.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很冷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.48,0:13:18.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,進來喝杯茶什麼的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.21,0:13:21.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才正說起你們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.16,0:13:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.62,0:13:25.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.45,0:13:30.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.47,0:13:32.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.77,0:13:39.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英學姐的作業也拖到今天了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.47,0:13:44.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作業？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.61,0:13:46.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吉野屋老師佈置的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.60,0:13:48.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個不是當作作業的剪貼畫…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.94,0:13:49.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.83,0:13:50.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是這麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.78,0:13:54.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你午休的時候在房間裡做作業呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.86,0:13:55.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.81,0:13:57.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼知道呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.66,0:13:59.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,靠推理啦  推理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.66,0:14:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後作業也及時地交上去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.47,0:14:04.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.85,0:14:05.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不然的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:07.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你就不會去玩雪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:09.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是沙英學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.50,0:14:11.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是敏銳的洞察力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:14.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮  這樣像隻貓一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.19,0:14:15.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喵～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.76,0:14:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不熱嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.36,0:14:19.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  擠死了擠死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:23.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經凍僵的身心都要融化了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.10,0:14:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.52,0:14:29.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英學姐  什麼時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:33.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來  為什麼是「碎片」？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.49,0:14:35.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.36,0:14:36.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:39.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡寫的是「PIECE」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.45,0:14:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.51,0:14:46.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.26,0:14:48.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說把我無限的愛化作碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.51,0:14:51.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,送到世界的各個角落去…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.59,0:14:53.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是寫錯了而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.26,0:14:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.86,0:14:57.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想調查一下到底有百分之幾的人能發現錯誤…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:15:00.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和你剛說的不是不一樣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.35,0:15:02.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全沒有發現
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.06,0:15:05.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮你莫非不擅長英語
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.81,0:15:12.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  連這個都有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.85,0:15:15.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看  小宮的兔子是茶色的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.48,0:15:18.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我做得太投入不小心混進了土…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:19.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.62,0:15:20.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是野兔？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.86,0:15:22.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.85,0:15:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.67,0:15:26.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.71,0:15:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.00,0:15:29.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  這個是摩艾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.92,0:15:30.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,摩艾？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.92,0:15:30.76,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（注：復活節島上的巨大石像）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.02,0:15:32.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過看著像是一個個的踏腳石而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.13,0:15:34.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尋學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:35.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.90,0:15:36.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:38.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是腦袋背對著我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.56,0:15:41.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其實這裡面放了垃圾箱喲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.95,0:15:42.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.53,0:15:47.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,順便說一下這是我做的雪人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.64,0:15:48.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不錯的作品呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.31,0:15:50.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是這麼晚回來的原因了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.32,0:15:53.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知不覺做得太投入了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.41,0:15:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英學姐你這照片是哪裡拍的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.11,0:15:58.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在二層向陽的走廊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.11,0:16:01.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那實在是個不錯的畫面所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我中途回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:05.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而沙英可是一直在那裡拍的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.15,0:16:06.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.05,0:16:08.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被偷拍了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.91,0:16:10.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼作為模特的報酬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.68,0:16:12.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給我些茶  蜜橘和脆餅乾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.87,0:16:14.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,順便再來些年糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.34,0:16:15.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.35,0:16:16.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在去沏茶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:18.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,桌上那些你先吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.50,0:16:23.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,托你的福我倒是拍著不少好的素材了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:25.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來只要把這些做成剪貼畫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.45,0:16:27.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在明天的實習課之前交上去就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.37,0:16:29.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.11,0:16:32.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英學姐還真能拖到最後關頭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.43,0:16:33.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來得及就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.42,0:16:36.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那  由乃你做的是怎麼樣的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.63,0:16:38.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.32,0:16:40.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,短信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.23,0:16:42.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吉野屋老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:43.82,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}收到的短信001  前一條/後一條\N吉野屋老師\N由乃同學  你的作業我看了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.33,0:16:44.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來  請喝茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.00,0:16:46.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  有勞了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:49.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同學  你的作業我看了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.41,0:16:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說臨時趕出來的  不過品味位不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.37,0:16:55.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,特別是把賀年片和照片做成剪貼畫這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.01,0:16:58.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你選的素材非常的不錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.65,0:16:59.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是素材好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.30,0:17:01.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.01,0:17:03.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你用的什麼素材？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.24,0:17:05.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.06,0:17:09.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在這個地方用了吉野屋老師的賀年片的copy
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.37,0:17:11.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,像這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.75,0:17:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.56,0:17:14.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…姿勢不對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.59,0:17:15.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.31,0:17:17.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我收到的賀年片是這樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.21,0:17:19.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我去拿來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:20.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.28,0:17:25.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.57,0:17:29.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.56,0:17:30.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.22,0:17:32.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能做到這份上也真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.01,0:17:34.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可怕的cosplay之魂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:38.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到底有多少種呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.77,0:17:40.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是班上人手一種…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.15,0:17:42.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我都想收集了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.14,0:17:43.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.86,0:17:44.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是她的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.34,0:17:47.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這份無以言喻才是可怕之處啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.64,0:17:52.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  另外一張賀年片呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.56,0:17:54.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,之前說的那張熱熱鬧鬧的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.25,0:17:54.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.14,0:17:56.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又是吉野屋老師嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.79,0:17:58.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.71,0:18:02.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,賀年片收到了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.99,0:18:04.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我在初夢裡看見了那一天的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.99,0:18:04.95,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（初夢：正月初一初二做的夢）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.03,0:18:05.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.90,0:18:06.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰發來的短信？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.57,0:18:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.59,0:18:09.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.16,0:18:10.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.13,0:18:20.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  我去繼續做剪貼畫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.43,0:18:21.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尋  謝謝你的茶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.43,0:18:24.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  我也差不多該…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:27.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的飯團真的十分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.38,0:18:30.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,非常的好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.51,0:18:32.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  尋同學的量…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.59,0:18:33.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.72,0:18:34.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.61,0:18:36.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尋在家裡吃多了年糕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.26,0:18:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.40,0:18:39.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要老是說這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.25,0:18:40.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.87,0:18:43.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天開始又要節食了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:45.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不努力可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.70,0:18:47.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多下來的食品  請務必給我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.16,0:18:49.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.59,0:18:51.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你白天不也說過這個話嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:52.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.96,0:18:55.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尋剩了一個飯團啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.45,0:18:58.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起去的食堂…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:19:00.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃在這裡做作業的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.22,0:19:04.56,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（今天的午餐菜單）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.22,0:19:04.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那時我還以為你真去拿落在家裡的東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.32,0:19:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要豬肉咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.32,0:19:08.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,加量的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:11.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要加料清湯麵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.82,0:19:13.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尋是兩個飯團
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.07,0:19:15.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後尋就對小宮說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.86,0:19:19.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「還是一樣吃著這看起來熱量很高的午飯呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮看著我的碟子說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.31,0:19:24.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「您的飯碗還真是輕飄飄呀」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:28.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是…你看…過年的時候年糕吃太多了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.43,0:19:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.96,0:19:33.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在家能飯來張口  真叫人感動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.09,0:19:34.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:35.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是問題所在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:38.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由於不運動  熱量不斷地囤積
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.28,0:19:39.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那年糕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:40.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一口咬下去就…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.97,0:19:42.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鬆鬆軟軟地…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.39,0:19:43.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鬆鬆軟軟…你聽我說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:43.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.78,0:19:44.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.82,0:19:47.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底重了多少公斤什麼的我都害怕得不敢問了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.65,0:19:49.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你這不是正在問嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.57,0:19:53.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由於這個原因又得稍微節食了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.03,0:19:54.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.75,0:19:56.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很出色地又把話題扯回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.76,0:20:01.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後尋學姐就剩了一個飯團
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.57,0:20:03.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼「由乃肯定沒有吃上午飯」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.23,0:20:06.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「這個就留給她吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.57,0:20:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.05,0:20:09.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是謝謝了  尋學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.28,0:20:10.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.87,0:20:12.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃你可不要被騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.86,0:20:15.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尋學姐是因為在節食才…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.10,0:20:15.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.25,0:20:16.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.85,0:20:18.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,食物有剩餘的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.33,0:20:20.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就捐助給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.47,0:20:22.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是想說這個的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.34,0:20:23.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.47,0:20:25.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尋學姐對人很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.63,0:20:27.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了不讓我操心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.81,0:20:29.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才這麼說的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.08,0:20:32.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃真是個好孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.30,0:20:34.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.78,0:20:35.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.59,0:20:38.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.88,0:20:39.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.09,0:20:41.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我並不是那麼出色的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:43.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係  沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.67,0:20:45.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃現在這個樣子就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.82,0:20:46.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.35,0:20:47.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,連尋學姐都…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.34,0:20:49.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪變小了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.48,0:20:54.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,趁再下起來之前  去一下便利超市吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.46,0:20:54.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.99,0:20:55.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.91,0:20:58.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.41,0:21:00.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的承蒙款待了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.81,0:21:01.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.16,0:21:03.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心些
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.17,0:21:07.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.98,0:21:08.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.10,0:21:09.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.96,0:21:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說有些早  晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.22,0:21:23.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.96,0:21:25.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還是亂七八糟一地的沒有收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.29,0:21:34.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.81,0:21:36.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,海之惠套餐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.47,0:21:38.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能中的話就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.06,0:21:46.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.51,0:21:48.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.04,0:21:53.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也發生了不少事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.02,0:21:57.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,手有些變紅了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.87,0:21:59.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,得搽些護手霜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.30,0:22:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,1月11日  完
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.35,0:22:10.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,待續
